2500|$|From 2003 until August 24, 2006, Shays was a [...] "stalwart supporter" [...] of the War in Iraq, {{and of a}} {{continued}} U.S. military presence there. Shay has faced {{a continued}} political challenge to his views in a district where recent polls show a solid majority of voters disapprove of the 2003 US decision to <b>invade</b> <b>Iraq.</b>|$|E
